Pre-requisite:-
Spring Boot
------------
	1. core java
	2. servlet/jsp
	3. Spring Framework
		- core
			1. di (setter/construction)
			2. bean lifecycle
			3. bean scopes
			4. bean factory post processor/bean post processors
			5. internationalization
			6. autowiring
			7. factory beans
			8. BeanFactory / ApplicationContext
			9. Annotations (@Autowired, @Scope, @StreotyeAnnotations, @PropertySource, @ComponentScan)
		- aop
		- tx
		- mvc
	4. Hibernate & Jpa api
		- Hibernate Core Objects
		- Hibernate Mapping File
		- Hibernate Configuration File
		- Get Vs Load
		- HQL
		- DML operations
		- ID Generators
		- Inheritance/Association Mappings
		- NamedQueries
		- Criteria api (optional)

Prerequisite:-
Microservices:
1. Spring Boot (should be very strong)
2. Restful services (Jaxrs api, Spring Framework restful services)
